data.description: Welcome to your new spacious oasis in sunny Florida! This impressive 3-bedroom, 3.5 bath pool home with an attached 2 car garage sits on an extra-large 16,800 sf double lot & is tailor-made for your large family's comfort and convenience. Plus, it comes with fantastic additional features, including a 2018 propane (Large Under Ground Tank) back-up generator with sub-panel & a detached cottage style apartment for extra income as a rental or a private place for extended family & friends. The cottage offers a front screened porch, a kitchen, bathroom with shower, a wall unit ac, an attic space with pull down ladder & a view of the back yard & pool.  As you step through the ornate Mediterranean-style double doors at the front entry, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light in the extra-large living room. This home is thoughtfully designed with a split floor plan, ensuring privacy and functionality for all family members.  Two of the generously sized bedrooms boast master suites, each complete with walk-in closets and private bathrooms, offering a serene retreat for everyone in the household. The third bedroom also has a spacious walk-in closet.  The kitchen itself is a chef's dream, featuring a large breakfast bar that seamlessly flows into the family room. A convenient pass-through window connects the kitchen to the rear pool porch/patio, making outdoor entertaining a breeze. The office space across the hallway with its plethora of cabinets, can also double as a kitchen pantry.   Step outside onto the expansive covered porch, complete with recessed lighting & plumbing for an outdoor kitchen. This inviting space provides easy access from the living room, master bedroom, and family room via sliding glass doors. It's the perfect spot for al fresco dining, relaxation, or hosting gatherings with family and friends.  Extras & updates include a lean-to covered barbecue deck, 2 side covered patios, a new in 2023 roof, a 2020 central ac, hurricane panels & electric screens & an electric pool heater.   Location-wise, you couldn't ask for better. This home is in the Whitfield community, which is well known for its world-renowned golf course & is situated within close proximity to both Sarasota and Manatee County, you'll have easy access to the Sarasota/Bradenton Airport, Downtown Sarasota, Ringling School of Art, University of South Florida, South College of Florida, Major Highways, Stunning White Sand Gulf Beaches, Boat Ramps, Golfing, Fantastic Shopping, a Wide Range of Restaurants, and Top-Notch Medical Facilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional Sarasota property your new forever home.  This home is in need of some cosmetics & updates, but due to the prime location, the homes square footage, amenities & extra-large double lot, it has tons of potential. Located in the Whitfield Overlay District.  Being sold as/is. Please note that room sizes are approximate.
